    {
      "start": 336.32,
      "end": 341.86,
      "text": "Wow, 제가 봤을 때는 우리 치코가 이 마지막 부분에서 명언 제조기입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.86,
      "end": 344.54,
      "text": "He's a maker of 명언"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.54,
      "end": 344.92,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.92,
      "end": 346.6,
      "text": "Maker of 명언"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.6,
      "end": 349.8,
      "text": "He's a man of wise words"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.8,
      "end": 350.08,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.08,
      "end": 351.82,
      "text": "Wise words, wise man"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.82,
      "end": 352.58,
      "text": "재밌네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.58,
      "end": 354.26,
      "text": "내용 한 번 알아보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.26,
      "end": 357.84,
      "text": "I just, I messed everything up"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.84,
      "end": 361.34,
      "text": "네, 에이브가 굉장히 좌절된 감정으로 이야기하고 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.34,
      "end": 364.3,
      "text": "I just, I messed everything up"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.3,
      "end": 367.62,
      "text": "저는 그냥 제가 다 망쳐버렸어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.62,
      "end": 370.04,
      "text": "Yeah, remember he sleeps in 치코's kitchen"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.04,
      "end": 370.46,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.46,
      "end": 374.94,
      "text": "And then he, on his way to work, when he goes to work, 치코 comes to work, he discovers"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.94,
      "end": 375.3,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.3,
      "end": 377.2,
      "text": "Abe's sleeping in the kitchen"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.2,
      "end": 378.86,
      "text": "네, 기억력 좋으시네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.86,
      "end": 379.92,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.98,
      "end": 381.3,
      "text": "I messed everything up"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.3,
      "end": 387.18,
      "text": "They fought, and fought, and fought, and yelled, and they just yelled"
    },
    {
      "start": 387.18,
      "end": 390.04,
      "text": "Oh, I can imagine how stressful he must have been"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.04,
      "end": 391.14,
      "text": "So stressed"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.14,
      "end": 391.72,
      "text": "So far"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.72,
      "end": 393.82,
      "text": "For a young boy to go through all that"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.82,
      "end": 394.2,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.2,
      "end": 397.28,
      "text": "얼마나 스트레스가 컸으면 이렇게 이야기를 했죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.28,
      "end": 402.04,
      "text": "They fought, and fought, and fought, and yelled, and they just yelled"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.04,
      "end": 402.6,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.9,
      "end": 407.24,
      "text": "그들은 싸웠고, 싸웠고, 싸웠고, 소리 질렀고, 또 소리 질렀어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.24,
      "end": 410.2,
      "text": "Oh, they didn't do anything productive"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.2,
      "end": 410.7,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.7,
      "end": 412.14,
      "text": "Except fighting and yelling"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.14,
      "end": 416.58,
      "text": "I mean, I think I just made everything worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.58,
      "end": 418.86,
      "text": "그러니까 제 뜻은요"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.86,
      "end": 419.4,
      "text": "I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.4,
      "end": 420.62,
      "text": "제 생각에"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.62,
      "end": 422.74,
      "text": "I just made everything worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.74,
      "end": 426.08,
      "text": "제가 모든 것을 더 나쁘게 만든 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.08,
      "end": 426.76,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.76,
      "end": 427.9,
      "text": "Ah, this is the problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.9,
      "end": 429.72,
      "text": "He's in his formative years"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.72,
      "end": 430.8,
      "text": "He's still developing"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.8,
      "end": 433.7,
      "text": "But he's blaming himself for his family's problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.7,
      "end": 435.36,
      "text": "자책하는 거 좀 위험한데, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.5,
      "end": 435.92,
      "text": "Very"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.92,
      "end": 442.2,
      "text": "네, 특히 worse라는 단어가 끝부분에 들렸는데, bad의 비교급이라고 생각하시면 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.2,
      "end": 444.38,
      "text": "Bad, better, worse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.62,
      "end": 444.9,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.9,
      "end": 445.62,
      "text": "No, no"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.62,
      "end": 446.14,
      "text": "Worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.14,
      "end": 447.5,
      "text": "Bad, worse, worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.5,
      "end": 453.88,
      "text": "Bad, worse, worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.88,
      "end": 455.04,
      "text": "Bad, worse, worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.04,
      "end": 456.5,
      "text": "Worst은 최악이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.5,
      "end": 457.08,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.08,
      "end": 458.08,
      "text": "Okay, thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.08,
      "end": 458.3,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.3,
      "end": 458.94,
      "text": "좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.94,
      "end": 461.1,
      "text": "Look, Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.1,
      "end": 463.9,
      "text": "네, 치코가 자상하게 이야기합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.9,
      "end": 465.14,
      "text": "Look, Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.14,
      "end": 466.84,
      "text": "자, 봐봐"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.84,
      "end": 467.74,
      "text": "Look, Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.74,
      "end": 470.9,
      "text": "You can't run away from your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.9,
      "end": 473.3,
      "text": "You can't run away from your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.3,
      "end": 475.3,
      "text": "아, 이 문장 진짜 좋은 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.3,
      "end": 476.16,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.16,
      "end": 477.34,
      "text": "되게 힘이 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.34,
      "end": 480.08,
      "text": "You can't run away from your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.08,
      "end": 483.38,
      "text": "너는 어떤 문제가 있다고 거기에서 도망칠 수 없어"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.38,
      "end": 484.4,
      "text": "도망치면 안 돼"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.4,
      "end": 486.32,
      "text": "You need to face it"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.32,
      "end": 492.2,
      "text": "Face가 여기에서는 마주치다, 마주하다 라는 동사적인 의미인 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.2,
      "end": 493.28,
      "text": "You need to face it"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.28,
      "end": 497.24,
      "text": "너는 그것을 마주해야 돼, 직면해야 돼 라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.24,
      "end": 498.72,
      "text": "You need to face your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.72,
      "end": 500.76,
      "text": "Head on, head first"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.76,
      "end": 502.08,
      "text": "떨려"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.08,
      "end": 502.94,
      "text": "I know"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.94,
      "end": 504.82,
      "text": "용감해져야 되는데, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.9,
      "end": 506.84,
      "text": "I'm scared too, but yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.84,
      "end": 508.56,
      "text": "We all need courage"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.56,
      "end": 512.0,
      "text": "We all need courage from a wise mentor like Chico, sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.0,
      "end": 516.8,
      "text": "Sometimes, people are not going to come together"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.8,
      "end": 520.62,
      "text": "Sometimes, 때때로, people are not going to come together"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.62,
      "end": 524.4,
      "text": "사람들은 서로 잘 화합이 안 될 때가 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.4,
      "end": 526.56,
      "text": "Just be yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.56,
      "end": 528.12,
      "text": "그럴 땐 어떻게 하라고요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.36,
      "end": 529.4,
      "text": "Just be yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.4,
      "end": 530.84,
      "text": "I agree 100%"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.84,
      "end": 531.32,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.32,
      "end": 533.62,
      "text": "Don't worry about what other people say"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.62,
      "end": 536.1,
      "text": "or if they're arguing or not"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.1,
      "end": 539.4,
      "text": "Just be yourself in all situations, if possible"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.4,
      "end": 540.74,
      "text": "너무 멋진 이야기입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.74,
      "end": 543.02,
      "text": "그냥 너답게 있으면 돼"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.02,
      "end": 544.54,
      "text": "그냥 너답게 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.54,
      "end": 546.08,
      "text": "라는 이야기예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.08,
      "end": 547.2,
      "text": "Yeah, 휩쓸리지 말고"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.2,
      "end": 547.58,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.58,
      "end": 548.86,
      "text": "그냥 당당 있어라"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.86,
      "end": 553.3,
      "text": "이게 굉장히 힘이 되는 그런 멘토로부터 얻는 조언 드리겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.3,
      "end": 555.92,
      "text": "이 내용 떠올리시면서 한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.92,
      "end": 558.42,
      "text": "I just, I missed everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.42,
      "end": 561.76,
      "text": "They fought and fought and fought"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.76,
      "end": 563.5,
      "text": "yelled and they just yelled"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.5,
      "end": 567.84,
      "text": "I think I just made everything worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.84,
      "end": 569.36,
      "text": "Well, maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.36,
      "end": 572.02,
      "text": "You can't run away from your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.02,
      "end": 572.52,
      "text": "You need to face it"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.52,
      "end": 573.58,
      "text": "You need to face it"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.58,
      "end": 576.94,
      "text": "Sometimes, people are not going to come together"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.94,
      "end": 578.6,
      "text": "Just be yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.6,
      "end": 582.86,
      "text": "You can't run away from your problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.86,
      "end": 584.04,
      "text": "You need to face it"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.04,
      "end": 584.98,
      "text": "Just be yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.98,
      "end": 588.42,
      "text": "이 문장들은 진짜 통째로 기억하면 좋을 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.42,
      "end": 590.2,
      "text": "마음에 새기도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.2,
      "end": 592.9,
      "text": "정말 위로도 되고 또 용기도 주는 문장들이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.7,
      "end": 596.68,
      "text": "우리 에이브 편 스크린 잉글리쉬는 여기까지고요"
    }
  ]
}